bark how many toys the toy box has

bark "Narrator: But after playing the cookies are now too temping, Bimba knocks the cookie jar onto the ground"
she whimpers as she wants and takes the first biscuit from her cookie jar

bark "Narrator: Bimba is not alone, there is also the dachshund Pepon"
I have a dachshund.
bark "Narrator: He is a bit simple and enters the room, tail already wagging."
Bimba shares with the dachshund

bark "Narrator: Bimba shared toys with Pepon (a miracle) and now looks at her remaining toys and says:"
when she has 3 toys then she howls "That was fine" otherwise she whines "I want it back!"

bark "Narrator: She decided to inform Pepon of how many toys she had left by barking."
she woofs how many toys she has

